            "title": "人行下周一開展4千億元人民幣MLF操作　較到期量少2千億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行公佈，為保持銀行體系流動性充裕，將於下星期一（4月27日）開展4000億元人民幣的1年期中期借貸便利（MLF）操作。此次操作規模較本月到期量減少2000億元，結束了連續13個月的淨增加勢頭。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15916973-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%80%e9%96%8b%e5%b1%954%e5%8d%83%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%a3mlf%e6%93%8d%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%80%e8%bc%83%e5%88%b0%e6%9c%9f%e9%87%8f%e5%b0%912",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_PBC-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 18:41:51",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
